          Docker (avec docker-compose),
        VMware, Linux,
        %strong
          PostgreSQL,
        MySQL, Oracle, MsSQL, RDS,
        %strong
          Ruby On Rails,
        Sinatra, Elastic Search, Delayed Jobs, Sidekiq, Redis,
        Gems: Devise, pundit,
        Tests: minitest,
        %strong
          Rspec
        Capybara, Cucumber
